snippet.title: MONSTER HUNTERS | Can a Secret Team Stop an Alien Invasion? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A mysterious crash releases creatures into the desert.
Stopping them may require weapons never used before.

When an alien prison ship crashes in the California desert, dangerous creatures are unleashed across the landscape. Conventional forces are quickly overwhelmed, leaving only one option: a secret government unit trained to fight threats from beyond Earth. With experimental technology and no real combat experience, the team must face an enemy unlike anything they’ve encountered before — and the fate of the planet hangs in the balance.

Director: Brendan Petrizzo
Cast: Tom Sizemore, Connie Jo Sechrist, Anthony Jensen.
